headline: Three Reasons We Are Fans of United Rentals (URI)
summary: United Rentals currently trades at $850 and has been a dream stock for shareholders. It’s returned 441% since December 2019, blowing past the S&P 500’s 92.7% gain. The company has also beaten the index over the past six months as its stock price is up 34.8%.
